
============================================================
                          README
============================================================

This is a README file generated by VMMGEN template generator.
The generated directory structure and template files by VMMGEN are shown here.

User need to fill required code wherever "ToDO: ". 
The generated code can be compiled with the following versions:
- Synopsys VCS Version C-2009.06 and later versions
- VMM 1.1 and later versions

*************************************************************
STEPS TO COMPILE AND RUN EXAMPLE
*************************************************************
vmmgen/proj/simple_dut_env/run $ make

Note: 
  1) To include the VMM inbuilt source from VCS installation:
     Inclusion of VMM_HOME can be replaced by ntb_opts rvm command in Makefile
  2) To use the VMM source other than VCS installation directory:
     Set environment variable VMM_HOME to the vmm-1.1 installation directory

